{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"4567915e-2acd-4a96-85d2-c6ba58dd5656","content":"Here's what you need to do:\n\n1. **Update package references** in your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <!-- Remove -->\n   <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.runner.visualstudio\" Version=\"...\" />\n\n   <!-- Add -->\n   <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.v3.runner.mtp\" Version=\"1.*\" />\n   ```\n\n2. **Upgrade xUnit packages** — MTP support requires **xUnit v3**. Replace:\n   ```xml\n   <!-- Remove -->\n   <PackageReference Include=\"xunit\" Version=\"2.9.3\" />\n\n   <!-- Add -->\n   <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.v3\" Version=\"1.*\" />\n   ```\n\n3. **Update your code** for xUnit v3 breaking changes (most tests work as-is, but watch for):\n   - `Assert.ThrowsAsync` return type changes\n   - `IAsyncLifetime.InitializeAsync` now returns `ValueTask`\n   - `TheoryData` and `[MemberData]` changes\n   - Namespace changes (`Xunit` stays, but some advanced types moved)\n\n4. **Enable MTP in your `.csproj`** (optional, enables `dotnet run` as test host):\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n     <EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\n5. **Run tests**:\n   ```bash\n   dotnet test            # still works\n   dotnet run             # also works with MTP enabled\n   ```\n\n**Key point:** You cannot use MTP with xUnit **v2** — the migration to Microsoft.Testing.Platform requires upgrading to xUnit **v3**. Check the [xUnit v3 migration guide](https://xunit.net/docs/v3-migration) for detailed code-level changes.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"117c5d51-92c0-4894-84ea-210442d5eacd","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user wants to migrate their xUnit.net project from VSTest (using xunit.runner.visualstudio) to Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP). Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge of this migration path.","outputTokens":527,"requestId":"5C37:3CEFF5:7F556:9FEF2:69F549F5"},"id":"356df894-ad2d-421b-8980-0a546a04b93f","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:49:04.807Z","parentId":"1b9196e2-5348-4745-96f1-f6b2c757e26f"}
